
In order to start developing on this, create a link in your 
~/.mozilla/firefox/PROFILENAME/extensions/ directory to this repo.  The link 
name should be the value of <em:id> in install.rdf.  So, it should be something 
like this:

~/.mozilla/firefox/PROFILENAME/extensions/cdep.illabout@gmail.com -> 
/some/path/to/this/git/repo/


Some good links for developing addons:
http://blog.mozilla.com/addons/2009/01/28/how-to-develop-a-firefox-extension/
https://developer.mozilla.org/en/firefox_addons_dev_guide
https://developer.mozilla.org/en/Extensions
https://developer.mozilla.org/en/Building_an_Extension
https://developer.mozilla.org/en/XUL_School
